feat(ux): v1.5.15 coachmark UX + brand icon + in-app i18n polish

Coachmark:
- step 4 (EJECT) spotlight Circle -> RoundRect to match v1.5.13
  rounded-square pictogram button.
- step 5 (settings) <-> step 6 (disguise) order swapped. Visual flow
  now reads left-to-right (eject->disguise icon->settings icon) and
  the tour ends on the "all controls live here" beat. primary labels
  moved accordingly: disguise=coachmarkNext, settings=onboardingFinalDismiss.

Brand icon:
- TopAppBar leading ⏏ glyph (Text "⏏") -> Image(ic_eject_button)
  in a Row alongside brandLabel. 28dp rounded EmergencyRed pictogram,
  matching the main EJECT button for consistent brand identity.

i18n:
- "언제 올까?" -> "얼마나 기다려?" / 7-language sectionDelay copy
  (How long? / 等多久？ / あとどれくらい？ / ¿Cuánto esperamos? /
  कितना इंतज़ार?). Korean triggerTimer also updated since both keys
  shared the Korean copy.
- Disguise picker dialog labels (calculator/memo/weather/clock) moved
  from Android resource (R.string.decoy_label_*, system-locale based)
  to AppStrings.kt (in-app language based) so that switching the
  in-app language actually translates the picker labels even when
  the device system locale stays in English.
  - 4 new fields in AppStrings: decoyLabelCalculator/Memo/Weather/Clock
  - 7 languages all populated
  - 8 stringResource() call sites in MainScreen.kt replaced with
    strings.decoyLabel*
  - res/values*/strings.xml decoy_label_* kept as-is (used by manifest
    activity-alias android:label, which IS system-locale based)

Working tree integration (was uncommitted):
- MainActivity.kt SplashScreen Composable: ⏏ Text(64sp) -> Image of
  R.mipmap.ic_launcher_foreground in a 28dp rounded EmergencyRed box.
- AppStrings.kt onboarding copy reframed (zh-CN/zh-TW/es) from
  military tone to friendly tone, aligned with Korean baseline.
- es unmask copy simplified.
- fastlane metadata refreshed across 7 locales for "비상탈출" rebrand.
- Legacy handoff/plan markdown docs cleaned up.
- Old V1 fake-call screens removed (V2 migration complete).

Build: tag v1.5.15 -> release-aab.yml trigger -> versionName 1.5.15
       (versionCode = 1000 + GITHUB_RUN_NUMBER).
No library deps changed.
